{"tid":1408122,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"大家 唔好輕敵 要記得 對準政府 五大訴求","createTime":"2019-08-04T16:35:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-05T08:18:42.000Z","uid":90601,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"0bcbe03774b606bf18d08d52a839d5919bfb2c90","tid":1408122,"uid":90601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T16:35:26.000Z","msg":"對唔住 可能你覺得我撥緊你地冷水<br />\n但大家要記得 今時今日政府仲係龜縮<br />\n今晚屌狗屌得幾過癮都好 政府依然可以唔讓步 然後推林統領依d傻鳩出黎死<br />\n<br />\n大家要記得<strong>五大訴求</strong><br />\n同埋 班狗一時唔行動 唔代表永遠唔行動<br />\n仲有水彩 仲有水炮車 甚至實彈未出<br />\n再悲觀d睇 政府背後仲有中共<br />\n我地要有長期抗爭既心理準備 唔好俾人拉 唔好受傷<br />\n適當時候 be water<br />\n<br />\n歷史會記得今年2019既香港<br />\n大家堅持落去 小心前進 一定會見到勝利既一日<br />\n<br />\n天佑香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"d6d57bf97e446502b9218dd3814a27b3d2088333","tid":1408122,"uid":90601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T16:39:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28206579b125f48ac610bbc6780e7e2601e2f177","tid":1408122,"uid":90601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T16:52:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9939bc6f46f55ae216a68772f0a94ebf0ab06b98","tid":1408122,"uid":90601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T08:18:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}